headline: Phillips 66 names Sean Maher as Vice President of Investor Relations and Chief Economist; Jeff Dietert to Retire
summary: HOUSTON, September 10, 2025--Phillips 66 announced that Sean Maher has been appointed vice president of investor relations and chief economist, effective Oct. 1.

headline: Phillips 66 agrees to acquire remaining 50% stake in WRB Refining
summary: The transaction, valued at $1.4bn, is subject to customary purchase price adjustments.
